TEXT.S: Yungkilu i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Yungkilu. u kasalumaluma' nu Yungkilu sa, 123 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 363 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 345 ku tademaw, pakalatu 95%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 18 ku tademaw, pakalatu 5%. u kasabinacadan, Paiwan 88%, Tayal 1%, Rukai 1%, zumazuma 3%.
